# Hierarchical trees (`@he-tree/vue`)

## When this applies

Renderer **hierarchical tree** (expand/collapse, nested folders, drag-reorder, branch checkboxes, etc.): project worlds, document browsers, template hierarchies, settings trees with nested groups.

## Required library (full replacement)

- **Use [`@he-tree/vue`](https://hetree.phphe.com/)** only (`BaseTree`, `Draggable`, helpers e.g. `walkTreeData`).
- **Never** Quasar **`QTree`** / **`q-tree`** anywhere ‚ÄĒ not small trees, prototypes, Storybook product previews. **`@he-tree/vue`** = **only** approved tree implementation.
- No new **`QTree`**; remove legacy **`QTree`** when touching surface.

## Imports and styles

```ts
import { BaseTree, Draggable } from '@he-tree/vue'
import '@he-tree/vue/style/default.css'
```

- Import default stylesheet **once** per tree surface (feature SFC or wrapper). Override in feature **`styles/`** SCSS with BEM + semantic tokens ‚ÄĒ do not fork library CSS wholesale.
- **`Draggable`** when users reorder nodes; **`BaseTree`** read-only or selection-only.
- **List DnD policy:** tree reorder = he-tree built-in only ‚ÄĒ **no** **`vue-draggable-plus`** on nodes ([fa-drag-drop-lists.mdc](fa-drag-drop-lists.mdc)).

## Virtualization (performance)

- Enable **`virtualization`** when tree may hold **~50+ visible rows** or deep expand-all paths.
- Tree or **bounded parent** needs explicit **`height`** or **`max-height`** (fixed px or flex child with constrained scroll). Virtualization fails on unbounded auto-height container.
- **`overflow: auto`** on **Draggable root** (scroll grows with content), not passive wrapper ‚ÄĒ see DnD scroll below.
- Combine with **lazy child loading** from SQLite on expand ([fantasia-sqlite-main](../skills/fantasia-sqlite-main/SKILL.md)).

## DnD + scroll (do not remount on reorder)

Playbook: [`.cursor/plans/he-tree-dnd-scroll-playbook_v2.4.14_2026-06-24-00-00-17.plan.md`](../plans/he-tree-dnd-scroll-playbook_v2.4.14_2026-06-24-00-00-17.plan.md). Reference: **`DialogProjectSettingsWorldTemplateLayoutTree`**.

- **No `:key` on `Draggable`** for sort-only changes ‚ÄĒ remount resets **`scrollTop`**; use **`treeData` + resync**.
- **Topology key** for resync: canonical sorted ids + membership ‚ÄĒ not draft array order or sort fields (**`mapDialogProjectSettingsWorldTemplateLayoutToTreeStructureKey`**).
- Topology match ‚Üí label patch in place; mismatch ‚Üí rebuild **`treeData`**.
- **No post-drop scroll restore** ‚ÄĒ fights **`virtualization`**; fix rebuild/remount instead.
- Append scroll: separate count watch; scroll container = he-tree root (**`resolveDialogProjectSettingsWorldTemplateLayoutTreeScrollContainer`**).

## Project layout

- **Thin Vue SFC** ‚ÄĒ template slots, `data-test-locator`, i18n **`$t`**, Quasar icons/buttons in **`#default`** node slots.
- **Feature `scripts/`** ‚ÄĒ tree data mapping, expand state, filter/search, DnD handlers ‚Üí Pinia/IPC.
- **`src/scripts/faHeTree/`** ‚ÄĒ shared pure helpers (flatten, walk, id maps) when ‚Č•2 features need same utilities.
- Types: repo-root **`types/`** (`app/types/...`); no colocated `*.types.ts` under **`src/`**. See [types-folder.mdc](types-folder.mdc).

## Styling and Quasar

- Node rows: Quasar **`q-icon`**, **`q-checkbox`**, **`q-btn`**, **`fa-text-*`** / **`fa-icon-*`** in **`#default`** slot.
- Scroll region: **`hasScrollbar`** when vertical scrollbar may shift layout ([`scrollbar.scss`](../../src/css/globals/scrollbar.scss)).
- **`data-test-locator`** on tree root + interactive node chrome ([vue-template-test-hooks.mdc](vue-template-test-hooks.mdc)).

